(11532, 95, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'Pearson is a well-known brand in the higher education space and MyLabs and Mastering were already successful products before Knewton partnered with Pearson to power their adaptivity.\r\n\r\nKnewton had to seamlessly integrate in a way that wouldn’t disrupt the product flow students were used to, while providing the robust learning benefits of our adaptive technology.'),
