(11596, 391, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', '<a href="#">Personal Math Trainer Powered by Knewton</a> is part of Houghton Mifflin Harcourt’s flagship GO Math! program and is the first K–12 product to combine HMH content with Knewton’s adaptive technology. '),
(11597, 391, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', 'field_57e0cd4b7a656'),
(11598, 391, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', '381'),
(11599, 391, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', 'field_57e0cd7c7a657'),
(11600, 391, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'Challenges'),
(11601, 391, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'field_57e37782762f1'),
(11602, 391, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'Houghton Mifflin Harcourt sought to build a product that could help address the national problem of mathematics proficiency for eighth-graders. According to the National Assessment of Educational Progress, approximately 75% of U.S. students are not proficient in mathematics when they complete 8th grade.\r\n\r\n<p class="big">They also endeavored to make a product that gives educators real-time insights into their class’ knowledge.</p>'),
(11603, 391, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'field_57e125ef62712'),
(11604, 391, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', 'To achieve this, the application needed to be equally easy and enjoyable for teachers and students to use. The concept was to give teachers more assistance in bringing each student to the same level of knowledge, while nurturing excelling students and keeping them from getting bored. \r\n\r\nBecause bringing students to a similar level was a pivotal product goal, Knewton had to come to the table with a robust level of adaptivity in order to provide the automatic remediation many students would require to perform at the eighth-grade level. This product also had to be aligned with Common Core standards and live up to the world-renowned Houghton Mifflin Harcourt name.'),
(11605, 391, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', 'field_57e1260962713'),
