(11787, 406, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', 'Pearson partnered with Knewton to create a product that could serve the unique student and instructor needs in higher education. MyLabs and Mastering are two of the most popular learning technology products available for higher education classrooms. Knewton powers the adaptive component of each product, known as the “Study Plan”in the MyLab portfolio and the “Adaptive Follow Up” in Mastering courses.'),
(11788, 406, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', 'field_57e0cd4b7a656'),
