(11955, 407, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'Pearson is a well-known brand in the higher education space and MyLabs and Mastering were already successful products before Knewton partnered with Pearson to power their adaptivity.\r\n\r\nKnewton had to seamlessly integrate in a way that wouldn’t disrupt the product flow students were used to, while providing the robust learning benefits of our adaptive technology.'),
(11956, 407, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'field_57e125ef62712'),
(11957, 407, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', '<p class="big2">There was also the challenge of making sure not to disrupt or add complexity to the instructor’s course plan, but give them added insight into their students’ preparedness and performance.</p>'),
