(12171, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', '203'),
(12172, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', 'field_57e0cd7c7a657'),
(12173, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'Challenges'),
(12174, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'field_57e37782762f1'),
(12175, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'Triumph Learning, the creators of Waggle, was primarily a print publisher since 1999. Transitioning to application development with a focus on adaptivity was a resource risk that Waggle was willing to take,  albeit with reservations.\r\n\r\n<div class="quote">\r\n<p>“Triumph historically has been largely a print publisher and when we decided to create Waggle, we really wanted to make it unique and different.”</p>\r\n<div class="author-name">Rick Noble</div>\r\n<div class="author-detail">CEO Triumph Learning</div>\r\n</div>'),
(12176, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'field_57e125ef62712'),
(12177, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', 'Waggle had the vision to design an app that was immersive, incredibly user-friendly, and motivating for young students. This involved incorporating kid-friendly graphics (in Waggle’s case, flying pigs that are set free when students do well). There was also a requirement to build a dashboard for teachers to use in order to gauge the progress of their classroom and give them the insights they need to intervene quickly when a student is struggling.  Doing both things well required two minds to meet two equally significant end users: the students and the teachers. \r\n\r\nWaggle had considered building adaptivity on their own, but ultimately chose to partner with Knewton. Because Waggle’s reputation with schools was at stake, the level of trust between their team & Knewton’s needed to be high for the partnership to move forward.'),
(12178, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', 'field_57e1260962713'),
(12179, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_approach_heading', 'Knewton’s Approach'),
(12180, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_approach_heading', 'field_57e37cf354f24'),
(12181, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_full_content', 'Knewton’s partnership with Waggle was quite deep. Waggle wanted adaptivity to be a shining feature of the product and this required the adaptivity to be robust and complete. “Adaptivity” can take many different forms in the marketplace, but Waggle and Knewton were in agreement about what true adaptivity meant and that it was the best option for helping students excel.\r\n\r\nKnewton also provided our best-in-class analytics. Waggle opted to make analytics readily available to instructors in an easy-to-use, and easy to act upon format.\r\n\r\nKnewton’s approach to building Waggle was built around delivering these 3, key product angles:'),
(12182, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_full_content', 'field_57e37d2154f25'),
(12183, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_icon_1', '403'),
(12184, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_icon_1', 'field_57e37dcb54f26'),
(12185, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_heading_1', 'Differentiated instruction:'),
(12186, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_heading_1', 'field_57e37de254f27'),
(12187, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_content_1', 'Knewton technology analyzes data to figure out what students know and what they need to work on, providing them with personalized assignments to help them meet course goals, master material, and get ahead.\r\n\r\n<em>Because this differentiation happens automatically, teachers can spend their time helping and inspiring their students.</em>'),
(12188, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_content_1', 'field_57e37df654f28'),
(12189, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_icon_2', '404'),
(12190, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_icon_2', 'field_57e37e2f54f29'),
(12191, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_heading_2', 'Gamified learning:'),
(12192, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_heading_2', 'field_57e37e3e54f2a'),
(12193, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_content_2', 'Waggle features games, review sections, progress indicators, and other features to keep students engaged and motivated in the learning environment.\r\n\r\n<em>Knewton met the product vision and delivered adaptivity within this gamified environment in a way that appeared seamless to the student user and just “part of the fun.”</em>'),
(12194, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_content_2', 'field_57e37e4a54f2b'),
(12195, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_icon_3', '405'),
(12196, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_icon_3', 'field_57e37e5b54f2c'),
(12197, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_heading_3', 'Instructor Insights:'),
(12198, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_heading_3', 'field_57e37e6754f2d'),
(12199, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_content_3', 'Waggle’s instructor interface uses Knewton analytics to provide teachers with actionable information about student performance. Educators can identify students who are struggling or excelling to tailor instruction accordingly.\r\n\r\n<em>Instructor Insights are always actionable and always in real-time.</em>'),
(12200, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_content_3', 'field_57e37e7554f2e'),
