(12270, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_heading', 'field_57e3776d762f0'),
(12271, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', 'Pearson partnered with Knewton to create a product that could serve the unique student and instructor needs in higher education. MyLabs and Mastering are two of the most popular learning technology products available for higher education classrooms. Knewton powers the adaptive component of each product, known as the “Study Plan”in the MyLab portfolio and the “Adaptive Follow Up” in Mastering courses.'),
(12272, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', 'field_57e0cd4b7a656'),
(12273, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', '389'),
(12274, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', 'field_57e0cd7c7a657'),
(12275, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'Challenges'),
(12276, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'field_57e37782762f1'),
(12277, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'Pearson is a well-known brand in the higher education space and MyLabs and Mastering were already successful products before Knewton partnered with Pearson to power their adaptivity.\r\n\r\nKnewton had to seamlessly integrate in a way that wouldn’t disrupt the product flow students were used to, while providing the robust learning benefits of our adaptive technology.'),
(12278, 413, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'field_57e125ef62712'),
(12279, 413, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', '<p class="big2">There was also the challenge of making sure not to disrupt or add complexity to the instructor’s course plan, but give them added insight into their students’ preparedness and performance.</p>'),
