(13141, 428, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_heading', 'field_57e3776d762f0'),
(13142, 428, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', 'Pearson partnered with Knewton to create a product that could serve the unique student and instructor needs in higher education. MyLabs and Mastering are two of the most popular learning technology products available for higher education classrooms. Knewton powers the adaptive component of each product, known as the “Study Plan”in the MyLab portfolio and the “Adaptive Follow Up” in Mastering courses.'),
(13143, 428, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', 'field_57e0cd4b7a656'),
(13144, 428, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', '389'),
(13145, 428, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', 'field_57e0cd7c7a657'),
(13146, 428, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'Challenges'),
(13147, 428, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'field_57e37782762f1'),
(13148, 428, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'Pearson is a well-known brand in the higher education space and MyLabs and Mastering were already successful products before Knewton partnered with Pearson to power their adaptivity.\r\n\r\nKnewton had to seamlessly integrate in a way that wouldn’t disrupt the product flow students were used to, while providing the robust learning benefits of our adaptive technology.'),
(13149, 428, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'field_57e125ef62712'),
(13150, 428, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', '<p class="big2">There was also the challenge of making sure not to disrupt or add complexity to the instructor’s course plan, but give them added insight into their students’ preparedness and performance.</p>'),
(13151, 428, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', 'field_57e1260962713'),
(13152, 428, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_pearson_approach_heading', 'Knewton’s Approach'),
(13153, 428, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_pearson_approach_heading', 'field_57e39f18b1de6'),
(13154, 428, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_pearson_content', 'In order to create a higher education product that would have a positive impact on both students and instructors, Knewton partnered very closely with Pearson to determine the best fit for adaptivity. The area in which it made the most sense to introduce an adaptive component was in follow-up assignments that could fit seamlessly into the existing Pearson MyLabs and Mastering products, challenge learners where they needed challenging, and offer the best content for each student based on what they know and what they need more help with.\r\n\r\n<h4>Study Plan</h4>\r\nFor MyLab courses, the goal was to offer supplemental, individualized support in the form of a personalized Study Plan. This would not disrupt the course flow as it currently existed and allow for those students looking for extra help to access targeted remediation within the product.\r\n\r\n<h4>Adaptive Follow-Ups</h4>\r\nIn Mastering Science courses, students apply what they’ve learned in class and from Pearson instructional material when attempting their homework. For students who don’t meet their professors’ predetermined threshold of success, an Adaptive Follow Up is assigned.The goal of these follow-ups is to bring each student to similar levels of knowledge and preparedness for class via additional practice, customized to reinforce concepts with which they’ve struggled.\r\n\r\n<h4>Meeting Professor Needs</h4>\r\nIn the higher education environment, you have many students that come from many different backgrounds, and who have potentially had very different learning experiences. Professors have the challenge of not only teaching their subject, but making sure very different students have a similar chance for success. Personalizing higher education students’ experiences with adaptive follow-ups gives students a better chance at succeeding in class regardless of their high school exposure, and it gives professors more time to inspire their students with a deep exploration of the concepts.'),
(13155, 428, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_2_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_pearson_content', 'field_57e39f2ab1de7'),
