(13447, 437, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', '<a href="#">Personal Math Trainer Powered by Knewton</a> is part of Houghton Mifflin Harcourt’s flagship GO Math! program and is the first K–12 product to combine HMH content with Knewton’s adaptive technology. '),
