(14483, 448, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_heading_3', 'field_57e37e6754f2d'),
(14484, 448, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_waggle_content_3', 'Waggle’s instructor interface uses Knewton analytics to provide teachers with actionable information about student performance. Educators can identify students who are struggling or excelling to tailor instruction accordingly.\r\n\r\n<em>Instructor Insights are always actionable and always in real-time.</em>'),
