(14494, 448, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_4_cs_results_image_content_block_0_cs_results_left_content', 'The district used Waggle to prepare more than 2,500 fifth through eighth graders for the South Carolina state assessment. After using Waggle, the number of students who demonstrated Proficiency increased 124% for the seventh grade, and 93% for the eighth grade.\r\n\r\n<strong>Source: <a href="#">Waggle case study</a></strong>'),
