(14506, 448, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_0_cs_case_study_structure_4_cs_results_image_content_block_1_cs_results_left_content', 'This district adopted Waggle in their third through eighth grade ELA classes. To prepare for the 2015 Missouri Assessment Program, 6,599 students used Waggle 3 times a week after school. Grade 3 saw a 16 percentage point improvement and Grade 4 saw a 19 percentage point improvement in the first district-wide adoption of Waggle.\r\n\r\n<strong>Source: <a href="#">Waggle case study</a></strong>'),
