(15091, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', '<a href="#">Personal Math Trainer Powered by Knewton</a> is part of Houghton Mifflin Harcourt’s flagship GO Math! program and is the first K–12 product to combine HMH content with Knewton’s adaptive technology. '),
(15092, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_content', 'field_57e0cd4b7a656'),
(15093, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', '381'),
(15094, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_1_cs_summary_image', 'field_57e0cd7c7a657'),
(15095, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'Challenges'),
(15096, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_challenges_heading', 'field_57e37782762f1'),
(15097, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'Houghton Mifflin Harcourt sought to build a product that could help address the national problem of mathematics proficiency for eighth-graders. According to the National Assessment of Educational Progress, approximately 75% of U.S. students are not proficient in mathematics when they complete 8th grade.\r\n\r\n<p class="big">They also endeavored to make a product that gives educators real-time insights into their class’ knowledge.</p>'),
(15098, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_first_column_content', 'field_57e125ef62712'),
(15099, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', 'To achieve this, the application needed to be equally easy and enjoyable for teachers and students to use. The concept was to give teachers more assistance in bringing each student to the same level of knowledge, while nurturing excelling students and keeping them from getting bored. \r\n\r\nBecause bringing students to a similar level was a pivotal product goal, Knewton had to come to the table with a robust level of adaptivity in order to provide the automatic remediation many students would require to perform at the eighth-grade level. This product also had to be aligned with Common Core standards and live up to the world-renowned Houghton Mifflin Harcourt name.'),
(15100, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_2_cs_second_column_content', 'field_57e1260962713'),
(15101, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_approach_heading', 'Knewton''s Approach'),
(15102, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_approach_heading', 'field_57e388049b368'),
(15103, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_full_content', 'Knewton worked closely with Houghton Mifflin Harcourt to deliver adaptivity and functionality across 4 main areas:'),
(15104, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_full_content', 'field_57e3875907ef8'),
(15105, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_points_0_cs_houghton_points_content', 'Take a complete look at each student’s interactions within the program in order to understand his or her strengths, weaknesses, preferences, and overall pace. \r\n\r\n<em>This information helps Knewton deliver the most personalized learning experience based on each individual’s needs.</em>'),
(15106, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_points_0_cs_houghton_points_content', 'field_57e387ae07efa'),
(15107, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_points_1_cs_houghton_points_content', 'Create personalized paths for each student so that everyone can achieve their goals in the way that’s most efficient and effective for them. \r\n\r\n<em>If learning needs are being met in real-time and at every juncture, students are more likely to stay engaged.</em>'),
(15108, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_points_1_cs_houghton_points_content', 'field_57e387ae07efa'),
(15109, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_points_2_cs_houghton_points_content', 'Provide recommendations to each student for the assignment they should work on next within the application. \r\n\r\n<em>This process is automatic and helps students continue to move through the course at their own pace.</em>'),
(15110, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_points_2_cs_houghton_points_content', 'field_57e387ae07efa'),
(15111, 463, 'cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_points_3_cs_houghton_points_content', 'Provide teachers with real-time insights into each student’s progress, so they can quickly intervene where necessary and adapt their lesson plans based on how the class is performing.\r\n\r\n<em>Teachers can use both their instincts and data to help their students succeed.</em>'),
(15112, 463, '_cs_content_blocks_1_cs_case_study_block_1_cs_case_study_structure_3_cs_houghton_points_3_cs_houghton_points_content', 'field_57e387ae07efa'),
